Intermediate CRS created to assist the emulation of the ETRS89 / HS2P1+14 SnakeGrid projected CRS through transformation HS2-IRF to ETRS89 (1) (code 9302) used in conjunction with the HS2-TM map projection (code 9301).

HS2 Survey Grid is equivalent to the tailored zero-distortion ETRS89-based SnakeGrid HS2P1+14, the Snake projection emulated using an NTv2 transformation (code 9302) and a Transverse Mercator map projection (code 9301).

HS2-VRF height is equivalent to ODN height as historically realised through OSNet v2001 and OSGM02. After the ODN realization was updated to be through OSNet v2009 and OSGM15, HS2-VRF height was introduced for backward consistency.
